There is now a mod menu for android go to the link below and download the Among-Us-Mod-Menu.apk its both the base game and a mod menu. Works with both 
google play services and MicroG.

To download the file from here

http://www.mediafire.com/folder/bajgbequzj9ef/Android

BackUp download Link (In case the link above doesnt work)

https://mega.nz/folder/Nl8hyAbI#cC0KgmhWo9J2EDaOSmbidA

Make sure if you have Among Us downloaded from the playstore you will need to uninstall it.
Tap on the .apk file and follow the on screen instructions.

Base game version - 2020.12.8 
